+Futures – Mini App Development Plan
+1. Project Overview
+
+Futures is a lightweight web/mobile application that allows users to share, view, and discuss cryptocurrency price forecasts. The goal is to create a simple, fast, and community-driven platform focused on short-term and long-term crypto predictions.
+
+2. Core Features
+2.1 User Accounts
+
+Email, Google, or wallet-based login (optional Web3 auth).
+
+Basic profile with username and avatar.
+
+User stats: number of forecasts, accuracy score.
+
+2.2 Forecast Creation
+
+Select a cryptocurrency (BTC, ETH, etc.).
+
+Choose forecast type:
+
+Short-term (24h)
+
+Mid-term (7 days)
+
+Long-term (30+ days)
+
+Enter predicted price and reasoning (optional).
+
+Set visibility: public or private.
+
+2.3 Forecast Feed
+
+List of predictions from users.
+
+Filters: by coin, timeframe, popularity, accuracy.
+
+Voting/likes or reaction system.
+
+2.4 Forecast Validation
+
+Automatic checking of outcomes when time expires.
+
+Accuracy score calculation (e.g., mean percentage error).
+
+Displaying “successful/unsuccessful” badges.
+
+2.5 Commenting & Discussion
+
+Comment threads under each prediction.
+
+Upvote/downvote comments.
+
+2.6 Notifications
+
+Forecast result notifications.
+
+New comments or likes.
+
+Trending forecasts.
+
+2.7 Admin Panel
+
+User moderation.
+
+Forecast moderation.
+
+Basic analytics.
+
+3. Technical Stack
+3.1 Frontend
+
+React / Next.js
+
+TailwindCSS or Chakra UI
+
+State management: Redux / Zustand
+
+3.2 Backend
+
+Node.js / Express or NestJS
+
+REST or GraphQL API
+
+Authentication: JWT or Firebase Auth
+
+3.3 Database
+
+MongoDB or PostgreSQL
+
+Redis (optional) for caching trending forecasts
+
+3.4 Crypto Data Provider
+
+CoinGecko API / Binance API for real-time prices
+
+3.5 Hosting
+
+Vercel or Netlify (frontend)
+
+Render, Railway, or AWS (backend)
+
+MongoDB Atlas (database)
+
+4. App Structure
+4.1 Screens / Pages
+
+Landing page — app description and login.
+
+Dashboard — personalized forecast feed.
+
+Create Forecast — form for adding predictions.
+
+Forecast Details — comments, likes, stats.
+
+User Profile — forecasts history, accuracy.
+
+Admin Panel — moderation tools.
+
+5. Development Stages
+Stage 1 — Planning & Design (1–2 weeks)
+
+Feature set finalization
+
+UX wireframes
+
+UI design in Figma
+
+Stage 2 — Backend Development (2–4 weeks)
+
+API structure
+
+Authentication
+
+Forecast CRUD
+
+Accuracy calculation engine
+
+Integration with crypto price API
+
+Stage 3 — Frontend Development (3–5 weeks)
+
+Building all pages
+
+API integration
+
+Responsive UI
+
+Stage 4 — Testing (1–2 weeks)
+
+Unit & integration tests
+
+Bug fixing
+
+UX refinement
+
+Stage 5 — Deployment (1 week)
+
+Deploy frontend + backend
+
+Domain + SSL setup
+
+Performance optimization
+
+Stage 6 — Launch & Iteration
+
+Beta testing
+
+Collect user feedback
+
+Add extended features (chat, leaderboards, etc.)
+
+6. Possible Future Features
+
+Web3 wallet login (MetaMask, WalletConnect)
+
+NFT badges for accurate predictors
+
+Social trading tools
+
+Real-time chat rooms for each cryptocurrency
+
+AI-generated forecast suggestions
+```
